      "text": "My favourite memory with my\nfamily is to taking mornings\nwalks during Spring vacation\nwhen we lived in pune. We really\nenjoyed the cool and fresh morning\nair . Some of my\nneighbours also would go for\na walk or a jog at that\ntime, am and we would wake\nto each other or exchange a\nfew words. We would stop by\nfor a cup of tea at our\nfavourite tea vendor's shop before\nreturning home. Those morning\nwalks would make us feel energetic\nfor the rest of the day. Now\nmy brother lives in singapore\nand I live in korea. Though\nthe spring season is beautiful\nhere I miss those morning walks\nwith my family."
    },
